:: Passive response — masc formal
You: "That's a fair point — we've been working to accelerate the timeline and this presentation reflects where we are now."

Marcus nods. The room settles. Your manager looks satisfied. The moment passes without incident.

//You smoothed it over. You are good at smoothing things over. You are not sure that is the same as being good at your job, but today, in this room, they appear to be the same thing.//

