A beat of silence. Marcus looks down. Your manager's expression shifts — just slightly — toward something that might be approval.

//You said the thing. The room is deciding what to do with it. You feel the difference between being heard and being tolerated, and you are not yet sure which this is.//

[[Board question — masc formal confident]]


:: Passive response — masc casual
